-[RIP] 295.

72
00:03:16.096 --> 00:03:17.798
-Cincuenta y ocho.
-[hombres gritando]

73
00:03:17.865 --> 00:03:19.933
Y 822.

74
00:03:21.869 --> 00:03:23.937
-[hombres silbando]
-[bramado]

75
00:03:24.838 --> 00:03:26.774
-[gruñidos]
-[línea sonando]

76
